KafkaCamelExample
-----------------------------
1.From the command Line move to KafkaCamelExample directory and build the Project.
2.Build Command: mvn clean install
3. Start the Zookeper ./bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties
4.  Now start the Kafka server:
   ./bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties.
5.To check the application on localhost,Use http://localhost:8080/KafkaCamelExample/kafkaworks.mvc
6.Now Type in the message, the message goes to the Kafka Topic and the Consumed Current Message is Displayed.
refer to Screenshots for the results.
7.Source: Java8
